@startuml
actor User
participant "Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Route Handler\nPOST /api/character-chat/messages" as Route
participant "Supabase Auth" as Auth
participant "Character Chat Service" as Service
participant "Character Repository" as Repository
database "Supabase DB\ncharacters, events, messages" as Database
participant "OpenAI API" as OpenAI

User -> Frontend: 캐릭터에게 메시지 입력
Frontend -> Route: POST /api/character-chat/messages
Route -> Auth: 현재 세션 확인
Auth --> Route: userId 반환
Route -> Service: 캐릭터 대화 메시지 처리
Service -> Repository: conversation과 캐릭터 정보 조회
Repository -> Database: characters, events, conversations 조회
Database --> Repository: character context
Repository --> Service: 캐릭터 대화 context
Service -> OpenAI: 캐릭터 응답 생성 요청
OpenAI --> Service: 캐릭터 응답
Service -> Repository: 사용자 메시지와 응답 저장
Repository -> Database: conversation_messages insert
Repository --> Service: 저장 결과
Service --> Route: 캐릭터 대화 응답
Route --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: 캐릭터 응답 표시
@enduml
